Package: scaleMultiply
Title: Scale and Multiply Utility
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xuan", "Li", email = "1208039950@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a utility function, `scale_and_multiply`, that scales a numeric vector to the range [0, 1] 
    and then multiplies each element by a specified multiplier. Useful for data normalization and transformation tasks.
